WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 33]

03:03.440 --> 03:05.900
[Jin Yao]

03:06.060 --> 03:07.650
The Ming bell rings

03:07.730 --> 03:09.260
and the soul lantern is out.

03:09.290 --> 03:10.250
That's not right.

03:11.120 --> 03:13.190
There is no war in Lanling today.

03:13.210 --> 03:15.130
Why would the soul lantern go out?

03:15.590 --> 03:16.310
Let's go.

03:16.329 --> 03:17.700
Let's go to the soul lantern room.

03:17.730 --> 03:18.800
Okay, let's go.

03:38.040 --> 03:40.190
Impossible... Impossible!

03:40.410 --> 03:42.610
How could our Sect Leader's soul lantern go out?

03:56.910 --> 03:57.840
Impossible...

03:58.530 --> 03:59.900
How could Sect Leader...

04:01.180 --> 04:02.120
No one can kill our Sect Leader

04:02.120 --> 04:03.990
and seniors in the entirety of the Eternal realm.

04:04.040 --> 04:05.650
No, no.

04:05.670 --> 04:06.340
This...

04:06.370 --> 04:08.010
This lantern must be broken.

04:08.030 --> 04:08.830
It must be a mistake!

04:08.860 --> 04:11.030
I don't believe it!

04:13.280 --> 04:14.590
The soul lantern is real.

04:15.470 --> 04:16.750
It's true that it's extinguished.

04:18.170 --> 04:19.850
If something really happened to Sect Leader...

04:20.800 --> 04:22.160
If he's alive, I want to see him in person;

04:24.460 --> 04:25.480
if he's dead, I want to see his body.

04:25.480 --> 04:26.530
Nonsense!

04:26.550 --> 04:27.600
I don't believe it!

04:27.630 --> 04:28.700
Impossible!

05:07.030 --> 05:08.620
Why is this happening?

05:08.880 --> 05:10.640
The Five Contemplations have been gathered.

05:10.670 --> 05:11.720
Why can't the power of the divine stone

05:11.720 --> 05:12.750
still can't wake you up?

05:31.920 --> 05:33.180
Fan Yue...

05:33.230 --> 05:34.720
Hang in there.

05:34.740 --> 05:36.180
I will save you.

05:36.950 --> 05:38.300
How is Master?

05:41.130 --> 05:42.350
Prepare the alchemy furnace for me.

05:42.380 --> 05:44.330
Why can't we save him when all Five Contemplations have already been gathered?

05:44.350 --> 05:46.080
Prepare the alchemy furnace for me!

05:48.420 --> 05:49.470
If you won't,

05:49.490 --> 05:50.159
I'll do it myself.

05:50.159 --> 05:51.280
Bai Shuo!

05:51.310 --> 05:52.710
Before you left,

05:52.730 --> 05:53.700
you would protect him with your life.

05:53.730 --> 05:54.930
I trusted you!

05:54.950 --> 05:56.950
You have to tell me what happened.

05:56.970 --> 05:58.560
How did this happen?

05:58.590 --> 06:00.270
If you want to be sad or ask who should be accountable,

06:00.290 --> 06:01.680
put them at the back of your mind for now.

06:02.560 --> 06:03.680
Prepare the alchemy furnace.

06:03.700 --> 06:04.730
I have to save him.

06:05.380 --> 06:07.040
Fan Yue can't die.

06:08.460 --> 06:09.980
I won't let him die.

06:23.670 --> 06:24.790
Master.

06:25.740 --> 06:28.230
Please bless me so that I can cultivate a first-grade elixir.

07:10.960 --> 07:12.530
The barrier is broken?

07:12.700 --> 07:14.680
It seems that the hidden power in Chong Zhao

07:14.700 --> 07:15.650
is not a coincidence.

07:16.420 --> 07:18.740
Did something big happen?

07:49.950 --> 07:51.220
Hidden power?

07:55.010 --> 07:57.060
Chong Zhao killed you.

08:03.540 --> 08:04.850
Seems like your secret

08:04.880 --> 08:06.440
is no longer a secret.

08:06.600 --> 08:08.740
But you deserve to die.

08:08.760 --> 08:09.730
Your death

08:09.760 --> 08:11.520
at least proves one thing–

08:12.530 --> 08:13.770
that the Divine Lord

08:14.240 --> 08:16.210
is finally coming back.

08:30.670 --> 08:32.429
Hidden power?

08:32.460 --> 08:35.309
You can control it?

08:35.330 --> 08:37.100
Who are you?

08:40.700 --> 08:41.870
Chong Zhao.

08:42.890 --> 08:44.200
Chong Zhao, how are you?

08:51.570 --> 08:53.290
I killed my master.

08:54.310 --> 08:56.000
I killed my master...

08:56.550 --> 08:57.120
It's okay.

08:57.120 --> 08:57.550
I killed my master.

08:57.550 --> 08:58.590
Calm down.

08:58.620 --> 09:00.310
We are no longer in Bodhi Village.

09:00.330 --> 09:01.850
We are in Bright Moon Palace.

09:01.880 --> 09:03.470
And Jin Yao is not your master.

09:03.490 --> 09:04.690
He is your enemy.

09:04.710 --> 09:06.470
He killed the Eternal Race.

09:06.500 --> 09:08.170
You killed him to save people.

09:08.190 --> 09:09.240
You did nothing wrong.

09:10.680 --> 09:12.770
I called him Master for 10 years.

09:14.680 --> 09:16.710
I... I killed him myself.

09:16.730 --> 09:18.200
-I...
-I killed him myself.

09:18.200 --> 09:19.240
I understand.

09:20.030 --> 09:21.030
I've also called Zhen Yu

09:21.030 --> 09:22.530
Master for 10 years.

09:22.560 --> 09:23.990
While seeing the truth

09:24.010 --> 09:25.370
is painful,

09:25.400 --> 09:27.040
it's not a bad thing.

09:28.310 --> 09:29.740
But with my power,

09:29.770 --> 09:31.700
how could I kill Jin Yao?

09:33.310 --> 09:35.110
I remember he mentioned something like the hidden power.

09:36.980 --> 09:38.340
You once said

09:38.370 --> 09:39.460
there is a power

09:39.480 --> 09:41.020
that is not demonic power on Zhen Yu.

09:41.040 --> 09:42.440
If my guess is right,

09:42.470 --> 09:43.600
that's hidden power.

09:44.000 --> 09:45.360
What he injected into your body

09:45.380 --> 09:46.620
was not only demon power,

09:46.650 --> 09:47.830
but also hidden power.

09:47.850 --> 09:50.210
Hidden power is the power of the Hidden Race from 60,000 years ago.

09:50.240 --> 09:52.330
It has long disappeared with them.

09:52.480 --> 09:54.410
Is Zhen Yu a Hidden Race from back then?

09:54.430 --> 09:55.530
Why did he inject this

09:55.560 --> 09:56.480
in my body?

09:57.830 --> 09:59.430
Maybe...

09:59.470 --> 10:00.440
Oh no.

10:00.460 --> 10:02.490
If Jin Yao died, his soul lantern would go out.

10:02.520 --> 10:03.760
Lanling would ring the Nether Bell.

10:03.780 --> 10:05.300
I have to send a message to Lanling

10:05.330 --> 10:07.120
to tell everything that happened in Bodhi Village.

10:07.140 --> 10:08.310
If anything happened to Sect Leader,

10:08.340 --> 10:09.900
Lanling would be in chaos.

10:20.070 --> 10:21.150
Chong Zhao.

10:21.330 --> 10:22.970
I hope you are not the third child

10:23.000 --> 10:24.450
Zhen Yu is looking for.

10:24.480 --> 10:26.250
I hope you have nothing to do

10:26.270 --> 10:27.820
with the Hidden Lord.

10:43.250 --> 10:46.010
[Master, I have something important to report.]

10:47.430 --> 10:48.630
I knew

10:48.630 --> 10:50.270
you would inform Lanling.

10:56.970 --> 10:59.590
[Jin Yao and Luan Zhu have been executed.]

11:08.810 --> 11:10.960
Do you think you can be peaceful

11:10.960 --> 11:12.610
in Bright Moon Palace?

11:12.630 --> 11:14.270
The plan has started.

11:14.300 --> 11:16.040
The end is coming.

11:16.070 --> 11:17.890
No one can escape.

12:03.730 --> 12:04.730
Why?

12:06.780 --> 12:08.660
Why is it still not working?

12:09.690 --> 12:12.050
Why can't I make it?

12:27.750 --> 12:28.630
Shuo.

12:29.050 --> 12:30.290
Take a rest.

12:35.310 --> 12:37.170
In Ning'an City,

12:38.670 --> 12:40.630
everyone called me the big bully.

12:41.820 --> 12:43.760
With my father's status

12:43.990 --> 12:45.650
and my wits,

12:47.120 --> 12:49.090
I thought I could do anything.

12:49.490 --> 12:52.450
I thought I was the best in the world.

12:54.410 --> 12:56.180
But I am nothing after all.

12:57.570 --> 12:59.270
Master gave me his tortoise shell,

12:59.300 --> 13:01.470
but I still can't make a first-grade elixir.

13:01.500 --> 13:03.270
I can't save Fan Yue and you.

13:04.130 --> 13:06.320
I really think I'm useless.

13:08.750 --> 13:09.690
Don't be

13:10.170 --> 13:11.560
too anxious.

13:11.640 --> 13:13.110
Don’t force yourself.

13:13.620 --> 13:15.500
The first-grade elixir's recipe has long been lost.

13:15.570 --> 13:17.170
It's not easy to make it.

13:17.970 --> 13:19.170
Even if you fail,

13:19.200 --> 13:20.480
it's not your fault.

13:20.500 --> 13:21.410
Okay?

13:22.260 --> 13:22.930
No.

13:26.450 --> 13:27.640
I can't give up.

13:28.880 --> 13:29.800
Xi.

13:30.670 --> 13:32.320
If I don't do my best

13:32.930 --> 13:34.600
to save you and Fan Yue,

13:36.000 --> 13:37.810
I will hate myself for the rest of my life.

13:53.200 --> 13:54.330
How is it?

13:54.360 --> 13:56.030
Any news about Sect Leader?

13:56.090 --> 13:58.120
I've sent my disciples to inquire around.

13:58.140 --> 13:59.590
There is no trace of Sect Leader.

13:59.840 --> 14:00.960
I haven't found

14:00.960 --> 14:02.200
any news about Sect Leader either.

14:02.420 --> 14:03.620
Why?

14:03.640 --> 14:04.840
How could the Sect Leader of Lanling

14:04.840 --> 14:06.470
disappear into thin air?

14:06.620 --> 14:08.900
I don't believe that Sect Leader is dead.

14:09.010 --> 14:10.250
Someone must have

14:10.280 --> 14:11.800
plotted this.

14:11.820 --> 14:14.010
When I find out who they are,

14:14.210 --> 14:16.170
I will kill them!

14:17.170 --> 14:19.860
Sect Leader went to look for Chong Zhao himself.

14:19.880 --> 14:21.720
But he didn't bring Chong Zhao back,

14:21.750 --> 14:24.130
nor did he even mention Chong Zhao.

14:24.250 --> 14:25.220
Could something

14:25.240 --> 14:26.970
have happened then?

14:27.000 --> 14:29.450
After Chong Zhao left Cold Spring Palace,

14:29.470 --> 14:31.780
he was still in contact with Sect Leader.

14:31.810 --> 14:33.450
We have never seen Chong Zhao.

14:34.110 --> 14:35.960
After such a big accident happened in Lanling,

14:35.980 --> 14:36.770
no matter what,

14:36.800 --> 14:38.400
we must summon Chong Zhao back.

14:38.420 --> 14:39.790
At least let him know

14:39.810 --> 14:41.380
something happened to Sect Leader and Senior.

14:41.410 --> 14:42.600
Cut the crap!

14:42.630 --> 14:43.720
Go look for Chong Zhao!

14:44.270 --> 14:44.790
Let’s go!

14:49.590 --> 14:50.710
Chong Zhao!

14:52.570 --> 14:53.690
Chong Zhao!

14:55.670 --> 14:56.400
He's not here.

15:00.300 --> 15:01.580
There's no dust.

15:01.610 --> 15:03.490
It means Chong Zhao lived here.

15:03.510 --> 15:04.870
He hasn't left for long.

15:04.900 --> 15:06.230
Come and take a look!

15:14.210 --> 15:15.660
This flower pattern...

15:15.970 --> 15:17.450
It's from Cold Spring Palace's Fu Ling.

15:20.470 --> 15:21.500
There are traces

15:21.520 --> 15:23.680
of female perfume in his cabinet.

15:23.710 --> 15:25.130
Could it be that

15:25.160 --> 15:27.040
Fu Ling lived here?

15:27.060 --> 15:29.060
What's going on between Chong Zhao

15:30.160 --> 15:31.710
and Fu Ling?

15:31.740 --> 15:32.870
No matter what,

15:32.870 --> 15:34.600
we must ask Chong Zhao for an explanation!

15:35.090 --> 15:37.760
When Sect Leader came to the steamed bun stall

15:37.780 --> 15:39.770
to look for Chong Zhao, did he notice Fu Ling?

15:39.800 --> 15:41.190
Why didn't he mention it?

15:41.210 --> 15:42.670
I always feel

15:42.760 --> 15:44.430
Sect Leader is hiding something.

15:44.460 --> 15:46.120
It seems that only by finding Chong Zhao

15:46.140 --> 15:47.930
can we know what happened.

15:58.660 --> 15:59.370
Xi.

15:59.850 --> 16:00.700
Xi.

16:01.000 --> 16:02.320
How are you, Xi?

16:04.420 --> 16:05.470
It's fine.

16:06.150 --> 16:06.960
It's fine.

16:06.980 --> 16:08.830
Shuo will be able to cultivate a first-grade elixir.

16:08.850 --> 16:10.540
Shuo will save you.

16:13.740 --> 16:14.760
It doesn't hurt.

16:14.990 --> 16:16.090
It doesn't hurt anymore.

16:19.560 --> 16:20.900
It doesn't hurt anymore.

16:21.480 --> 16:22.690
It's the alchemy furnace!

16:27.110 --> 16:28.170
I made it!

16:29.360 --> 16:30.430
A first-grade elixir.

16:30.650 --> 16:31.860
I made it!

17:04.030 --> 17:04.619
Xi.

17:04.660 --> 17:05.670
Xi.

17:14.720 --> 17:15.520
-Xi!
-Xi!

17:20.619 --> 17:22.069
What I just spit out

17:22.530 --> 17:23.849
was poisonous blood.

17:23.869 --> 17:25.140
I can feel

17:25.170 --> 17:26.849
the spiritual vein in my body is smooth

17:26.869 --> 17:28.150
and the pain disappearing.

17:29.570 --> 17:30.460
Shuo.

17:31.690 --> 17:32.630
Chong Zhao.

17:33.440 --> 17:34.760
My body has been detoxified

17:36.380 --> 17:37.340
of the Heart Devouring Poison.

18:19.090 --> 18:20.700
The Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal

18:20.720 --> 18:22.730
is caused by the cultivation of demonic magic.

18:22.910 --> 18:24.550
It's unlike Heart Devouring Poison.

18:25.180 --> 18:26.010
If...

18:27.170 --> 18:29.800
If this first-grade elixir can’t save him,

18:29.820 --> 18:31.300
what should we do?

18:31.330 --> 18:32.660
I don't think about ifs.

18:33.410 --> 18:36.000
I just do my best.

18:36.530 --> 18:38.490
I believe he will wake up.

18:39.230 --> 18:40.430
He said

18:41.000 --> 18:42.480
he wouldn't leave me alone.

18:42.770 --> 18:49.660
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

18:50.150 --> 18:56.040
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

18:57.480 --> 19:00.280
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

19:01.270 --> 19:04.650
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

19:05.230 --> 19:11.480
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

19:05.660 --> 19:07.990
Maybe one first-grade elixir is not enough.

19:08.960 --> 19:10.290
I'll continue to make more.

19:11.910 --> 19:18.870
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

19:19.550 --> 19:26.050
♫All the answers are already explained♫

19:27.350 --> 19:29.970
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

19:30.500 --> 19:33.710
♫But we're destined to part♫

19:34.590 --> 19:40.550
♫How can I downplay this?♫

19:41.290 --> 19:44.490
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

19:44.990 --> 19:47.870
♫When my star falls only for you♫

19:48.440 --> 19:50.210
♫When the heavens fall♫

19:50.710 --> 19:55.720
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

19:56.120 --> 19:58.910
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

19:59.760 --> 20:03.480
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

20:04.370 --> 20:13.020
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

20:35.450 --> 20:40.210
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

20:43.200 --> 20:48.430
♫All the answers are already explained♫

20:48.370 --> 20:50.050
I heard from the demons that

20:50.740 --> 20:53.150
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

20:51.980 --> 20:54.400
a bear demon from Donglu, Polar Region,

20:54.050 --> 20:56.980
♫But we're destined to part♫

20:54.420 --> 20:55.720
and a panther demon from Sun Mountain

20:55.720 --> 20:57.590
fell in love with the same girl.

20:57.690 --> 21:03.110
♫How can I downplay this?♫

20:58.320 --> 21:00.280
Thus, they fought.

21:00.340 --> 21:02.660
The Bird Clan and Moth Clan

21:02.800 --> 21:04.550
burned bridges because they fought over

21:03.620 --> 21:06.870
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

21:04.550 --> 21:05.830
caterpillars,

21:06.450 --> 21:08.530
saying they would never talk to each other again.

21:07.460 --> 21:10.370
♫When my star falls only for you♫

21:08.570 --> 21:09.610
The leader of the Rat Clan

21:09.640 --> 21:11.790
took bribes in your name

21:11.370 --> 21:12.660
♫When the heavens fall♫

21:12.530 --> 21:13.920
and was imprisoned.

21:13.250 --> 21:18.180
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

21:14.560 --> 21:16.120
He even cried for injustice every day.

21:17.190 --> 21:17.950
Look.

21:18.760 --> 21:21.460
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

21:20.360 --> 21:23.390
There are so many things waiting for you to deal with in Bright Moon Palace.

21:22.230 --> 21:26.060
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

21:24.190 --> 21:25.880
How can the Demon King

21:25.900 --> 21:27.690
slack off?

21:26.770 --> 21:34.320
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

21:27.720 --> 21:29.440
All demons in the Polar Region are waiting for you.

21:30.790 --> 21:32.230
I'm waiting for you too.

21:35.140 --> 21:38.520
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

21:35.460 --> 21:37.020
I thought

21:39.010 --> 21:40.730
as long as the Five Contemplations are gathered

21:39.480 --> 21:41.500
♫When my star falls only for you♫

21:42.220 --> 21:43.750
I can save you.

21:42.340 --> 21:44.030
♫When the heavens fall♫

21:44.560 --> 21:49.110
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

21:45.000 --> 21:46.200
But it turns out...

21:48.520 --> 21:49.890
That was just my wishful thinking.

21:50.000 --> 21:52.750
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

21:51.400 --> 21:52.590
But Fan Yue...

21:53.430 --> 21:57.480
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

21:56.560 --> 21:58.120
Please wake up

21:58.560 --> 22:08.250
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

21:58.920 --> 22:00.000
for me.

22:01.510 --> 22:02.680
Okay?

22:45.350 --> 22:46.390
Fan Yue.

22:49.790 --> 22:51.460
I dreamed of you again.

22:55.310 --> 22:58.460
When will you wake up?

22:59.200 --> 23:02.720
What else can I do to wake you up?

23:02.780 --> 23:03.850
Shuo.

23:23.220 --> 23:24.420
It's not a dream.

23:32.810 --> 23:33.770
Fan Yue.

23:35.470 --> 23:37.100
Is it really you?

23:38.810 --> 23:39.810
You're awake.

23:42.320 --> 23:47.240
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

23:48.690 --> 23:50.080
It's me, Shuo.

23:50.440 --> 23:56.050
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

23:51.000 --> 23:52.300
I'm back.

23:58.730 --> 24:06.380
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

24:03.080 --> 24:06.050
I thought you would never wake up again.

24:07.160 --> 24:12.500
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

24:07.600 --> 24:08.900
It's all my fault.

24:08.950 --> 24:09.820
Be good.

24:10.500 --> 24:11.490
Don't cry.

24:17.330 --> 24:18.340
So...

24:19.030 --> 24:21.060
You were cured by the first-grade elixir?

24:21.430 --> 24:22.840
You woke me up.

24:22.860 --> 24:23.720
I thought

24:23.400 --> 24:26.640
♫Across thousands of miles♫

24:23.720 --> 24:25.550
I would really leave this time.

24:26.420 --> 24:28.840
But suddenly, a force stopped me.

24:29.830 --> 24:31.800
I heard everything you said.

24:31.520 --> 24:36.330
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

24:32.210 --> 24:34.120
I can't leave you.

24:36.490 --> 24:38.080
I'm back.

24:39.250 --> 24:46.100
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

24:43.840 --> 24:45.050
Since you're back...

24:46.460 --> 24:47.980
Since you don't want to leave...

24:47.220 --> 24:52.260
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

24:48.350 --> 24:49.720
promise me

24:50.860 --> 24:52.650
that you will never leave me,

24:52.680 --> 24:53.720
okay?

24:54.330 --> 24:55.080
Okay.

24:56.700 --> 24:58.090
I promise you.

24:57.170 --> 24:59.070
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

24:58.990 --> 25:01.330
I will never leave you.

24:59.400 --> 25:01.370
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

25:01.430 --> 25:03.220
♫My love brought tears♫

25:03.470 --> 25:05.190
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

25:05.610 --> 25:07.440
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

25:07.650 --> 25:09.070
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

25:09.280 --> 25:10.900
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

25:11.270 --> 25:13.250
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

25:24.430 --> 25:25.600
Should I

25:25.900 --> 25:28.550
call you Bai Xi or Fu Ling?

25:29.450 --> 25:31.500
They are just names.

25:31.530 --> 25:32.530
It's up to you.

25:34.430 --> 25:36.880
Every time we met, we'd be at each other's necks.

25:37.530 --> 25:38.680
I never thought I could

25:38.700 --> 25:40.460
talk to you so calmly.

25:41.000 --> 25:42.870
I used to think

25:42.890 --> 25:45.460
I would only come here for one reason:

25:45.550 --> 25:47.390
to attack Bright Moon Palace.

25:47.410 --> 25:48.400
What a coincidence.

25:48.830 --> 25:51.010
I used to only think of

25:51.040 --> 25:52.730
destroying Cold Spring.

25:59.750 --> 26:00.590
Tian Huo.

26:02.610 --> 26:03.420
I'm sorry.

26:06.660 --> 26:07.830
I'm sorry for what heppened

26:07.860 --> 26:09.210
in the Outlanders' City

26:09.230 --> 26:10.540
and at the Fox Clan.

26:10.560 --> 26:12.360
I killed your family

26:12.390 --> 26:13.590
and those you love.

26:21.340 --> 26:22.580
I should atone

26:22.610 --> 26:23.830
for my sins.

26:24.220 --> 26:25.990
So you came to me today

26:26.170 --> 26:27.650
to seek death?

26:27.680 --> 26:29.130
Atonement,

26:29.370 --> 26:30.500
not death.

26:32.110 --> 26:33.870
You think I wouldn't kill you?

26:35.150 --> 26:36.350
I didn't tell anyone

26:36.350 --> 26:37.650
I asked you to meet here.

26:37.680 --> 26:38.480
No one will know

26:38.500 --> 26:39.790
what you do.

26:41.650 --> 26:44.280
I have thought about killing you more than once.

26:47.110 --> 26:48.440
But your life

26:48.440 --> 26:50.310
was saved by Bai Shuo.

26:50.940 --> 26:52.770
Bai Shuo saved Master.

26:52.810 --> 26:54.350
I appreciate her kindness.

26:55.220 --> 26:56.400
I don't want to make things difficult for her

26:56.400 --> 26:58.000
nor make things difficult for Master.

27:00.040 --> 27:01.450
Don't mention

27:01.670 --> 27:02.790
what shouldn't be mentioned in the future.

27:07.260 --> 27:08.620
What are you waiting for?

27:09.020 --> 27:10.290
Take the dagger back.

27:23.280 --> 27:23.910
I'm sorry.

27:25.230 --> 27:26.150
And...

27:27.060 --> 27:27.820
Thank you.

27:34.190 --> 27:35.950
I think I know

27:36.040 --> 27:37.450
what's behind Jin Yao's death.

27:37.690 --> 27:39.770
The hidden power in Chong Zhao

27:39.790 --> 27:40.960
was given by Zhen Yu.

27:42.210 --> 27:43.470
Have you heard of

27:43.490 --> 27:44.930
how to dissolve the hidden power?

27:45.530 --> 27:47.110
Hidden power

27:47.340 --> 27:49.580
goes back to ancient Divine Region.

27:49.800 --> 27:51.440
I don't know more than you.

27:52.050 --> 27:54.160
Back then, the Hidden Lord tried to destroy the world.

27:54.190 --> 27:55.560
He took spiritual power

27:55.580 --> 27:56.860
through hidden power.

27:56.930 --> 27:58.140
Even today,

27:58.270 --> 28:00.310
various tribes are still scared of the hidden power.

28:00.860 --> 28:02.030
So,

28:02.370 --> 28:04.360
the fact that Chong Zhao has the hidden power

28:04.610 --> 28:06.050
has to be kept a secret.

28:17.000 --> 28:18.590
Why are you staring at me like that?

28:18.620 --> 28:20.030
Aren’t you going back to rest?

28:20.140 --> 28:22.010
Although your Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal is gone,

28:22.040 --> 28:24.440
it will take some time to recover.

28:24.460 --> 28:26.140
I'm afraid you won't take the medicine.

28:26.230 --> 28:28.360
Are you afraid that I won't take the medicine

28:28.470 --> 28:30.190
or are you reluctant to leave me?

28:30.310 --> 28:32.420
I just want to be with you.

28:32.440 --> 28:33.200
What's wrong with that?

28:35.540 --> 28:38.030
You are just like the

28:36.530 --> 28:40.060
♫The person standing far away♫

28:38.150 --> 28:40.060
the domineering Bai Shuo I first met.

28:40.140 --> 28:41.940
You're not much better.

28:40.940 --> 28:42.630
♫Don't be afraid♫

28:42.040 --> 28:43.650
The invincible Demon King.

28:43.680 --> 28:44.750
When we first met,

28:43.960 --> 28:47.950
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

28:44.790 --> 28:46.060
you wanted to bite me.

28:48.810 --> 28:55.220
♫Walk towards me♫

28:51.460 --> 28:53.220
Cang Shan was still around back then.

28:54.230 --> 28:56.580
We met a lot of people

28:56.610 --> 28:57.890
and went through a lot.

28:57.250 --> 28:59.800
♫My heart feels so...♫

28:59.310 --> 29:00.610
There's also Ling Long,

29:00.630 --> 29:02.020
Rong Xian,

29:00.660 --> 29:06.260
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

29:02.180 --> 29:03.290
Mu Jiu,

29:03.700 --> 29:04.660
and Master.

29:06.400 --> 29:08.290
Sometimes I think

29:08.210 --> 29:11.850
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

29:08.340 --> 29:10.640
if I didn't want to be an immortal,

29:10.860 --> 29:12.470
and didn't try gathering the Five Contemplations,

29:12.490 --> 29:13.920
would all these

29:13.920 --> 29:15.440
have not happened?

29:16.110 --> 29:18.780
♫You are my distant call♫

29:16.380 --> 29:17.830
Then they wouldn't have...

29:19.870 --> 29:24.030
♫You are my first and last♫

29:22.320 --> 29:23.070
Shuo.

29:23.790 --> 29:26.170
Everyone has their own fate.

29:24.970 --> 29:30.490
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

29:26.550 --> 29:28.230
Even without you,

29:28.260 --> 29:30.010
some things would happen.

29:30.850 --> 29:31.840
You have to believe

29:31.320 --> 29:34.010
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

29:32.490 --> 29:33.840
those who left,

29:33.860 --> 29:35.580
as long as we don't forget them,

29:34.860 --> 29:39.510
♫Let's never let go♫

29:35.610 --> 29:37.410
then they have never left.

29:44.790 --> 29:46.000
Fortunately, you are still here.

29:46.800 --> 29:49.390
Xi and Chong Zhao are also in Bright Moon Palace.

29:49.410 --> 29:51.460
Although Chong Zhao has hidden power,

29:51.890 --> 29:54.540
I believe we can find a way to dissolve it.

29:54.570 --> 29:56.090
Everything

29:56.110 --> 29:58.190
will turn out fine,

29:58.220 --> 29:59.510
right?

29:58.820 --> 30:02.540
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

29:59.530 --> 30:00.640
It will.

30:01.510 --> 30:03.530
You have the Five Contemplations now.

30:03.550 --> 30:05.930
The power of the Contemplation Stone is taking shape too.

30:03.560 --> 30:05.560
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

30:06.500 --> 30:08.700
You will continue to become stronger.

30:06.530 --> 30:09.850
♫The one who was slightly late♫

30:08.720 --> 30:10.150
When you become stronger,

30:10.250 --> 30:11.880
you may face a new challenge.

30:11.000 --> 30:18.020
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

30:12.940 --> 30:14.510
But no matter what the future holds,

30:14.540 --> 30:16.160
you must always

30:16.190 --> 30:18.580
be the free Bai Shuo.

30:19.420 --> 30:26.260
♫You enriched my life♫

30:26.540 --> 30:30.310
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

30:27.240 --> 30:28.420
It's almost anniversary

30:28.760 --> 30:30.030
of the establishment of Bright Moon Palace

30:30.030 --> 30:31.550
by Tian Huo, Cang Shan, and me.

30:32.080 --> 30:33.160
We'd celebrate within the palace

30:33.160 --> 30:34.700
for the anniversary every year.

30:34.190 --> 30:37.970
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

30:34.730 --> 30:35.730
I'll go arrange for it.

30:36.810 --> 30:38.320
You just recovered.

30:38.350 --> 30:39.870
You should take a good rest.

30:38.910 --> 30:43.000
♫You are my determined way home♫

30:39.890 --> 30:41.410
I'll prepare it this time.

30:41.440 --> 30:42.440
After all these obstacles,

30:42.460 --> 30:43.910
I also found Xi.

30:43.940 --> 30:45.180
Let's hold a gathering

30:44.030 --> 30:49.080
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

30:45.210 --> 30:46.100
for everyone

30:46.120 --> 30:47.320
to make peace for next year.

30:47.350 --> 30:49.460
Do you know how to prepare the celebration of a Demon Race?

30:49.480 --> 30:50.760
It's all the same thing.

30:49.940 --> 30:53.440
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

30:51.350 --> 30:52.840
Just wait and see.

30:52.860 --> 30:55.150
I will give you the most unforgettable celebration.

30:54.250 --> 30:56.250
♫Let's never let go♫

31:24.060 --> 31:25.210
It's cold at night.

31:25.240 --> 31:26.790
Why are you sitting here alone?

31:26.810 --> 31:28.680
I'm just doing some reflection.

31:28.710 --> 31:29.630
In the past,

31:29.650 --> 31:30.730
you were an immortal;

31:30.760 --> 31:32.440
you were irreconcilable with the Demon Race.

31:32.500 --> 31:34.130
I was the Young Lord of Cold Spring Palace.

31:34.160 --> 31:35.940
There's only one possibility between me and Fan Yue:

31:36.000 --> 31:37.520
only one of us can live.

31:38.170 --> 31:39.450
I didn’t expect

31:39.570 --> 31:41.130
the Bright Moon Palace

31:41.160 --> 31:43.110
to be the only place that can protect us now,

31:43.220 --> 31:44.620
and that Fan Yue and us

31:44.650 --> 31:46.140
would become friends.

31:46.160 --> 31:47.190
My parents,

31:47.220 --> 31:49.110
Master and seniors taught me that

31:49.130 --> 31:50.240
eternals and demons are irreconcilable

31:50.270 --> 31:51.670
like water and fire.

31:52.780 --> 31:54.120
But in fact, you were a human,

31:54.150 --> 31:55.530
but you became a demon.

31:55.770 --> 31:56.820
I'm an immortal,

31:56.850 --> 31:58.850
but I have demonic power and hidden power.

31:58.870 --> 31:59.900
Fan Yue is a demon,

31:59.930 --> 32:01.620
but he protects everyone.

32:01.640 --> 32:02.800
Shuo is human,

32:02.830 --> 32:04.150
but she's as strong as eternals and demons.

32:05.640 --> 32:07.030
It doesn't matter

32:07.030 --> 32:08.000
what we are.

32:08.400 --> 32:09.530
What matters is

32:10.910 --> 32:12.580
what we choose to be.

32:13.370 --> 32:14.940
Judging from what you said,

32:14.970 --> 32:16.490
you seem to be implying something.

32:19.190 --> 32:20.990
I know you're worried about me

32:21.010 --> 32:22.410
and my hidden power,

32:22.440 --> 32:24.180
afraid I'll be controlled by it.

32:24.200 --> 32:25.200
Don't worry.

32:25.230 --> 32:26.760
I won't be controlled by my hidden power.

32:27.690 --> 32:29.060
I know who I am

32:29.090 --> 32:31.160
and what I should do.

32:31.920 --> 32:33.360
I won't let you down.

32:35.560 --> 32:37.000
Of course I trust you.

32:37.020 --> 32:39.060
The Chong Zhao I know

32:39.090 --> 32:41.270
is upright and righteous,

32:41.300 --> 32:43.610
kind and unyielding.

32:43.630 --> 32:45.900
How could he be affected by his hidden power?

32:50.130 --> 32:51.290
Guess

32:51.480 --> 32:52.690
what I'm thinking.

32:57.070 --> 32:59.570
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

32:57.160 --> 32:58.190
-The steamed bun stall.
-The steamed bun stall.

33:00.540 --> 33:02.850
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

33:03.310 --> 33:04.790
I often think of

33:03.710 --> 33:07.520
♫I remember that word of concern♫

33:04.810 --> 33:06.720
when you taught me how to make steamed buns.

33:07.430 --> 33:08.520
Chong Zhao.

33:08.070 --> 33:11.280
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

33:09.090 --> 33:11.250
I miss the days in Ning'an City.

33:11.750 --> 33:14.870
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

33:15.480 --> 33:18.760
♫It dried in the wind♫

33:18.710 --> 33:20.350
When everything is settled,

33:19.280 --> 33:21.070
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

33:21.510 --> 33:22.750
I'll take you home.

33:21.790 --> 33:25.180
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

33:25.840 --> 33:27.640
But with only the two of us in the steamed bun stall,

33:26.090 --> 33:29.470
♫That year, that year♫

33:27.640 --> 33:28.930
it would be boring.

33:29.160 --> 33:30.050
Shall we

33:30.070 --> 33:31.380
have a few children?

33:30.280 --> 33:33.370
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

33:31.910 --> 33:32.950
How about two?

33:32.970 --> 33:34.260
One like you...

33:33.920 --> 33:37.240
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

33:38.070 --> 33:40.820
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

33:39.020 --> 33:40.930
Who said I was going to have babies wit you?

33:41.520 --> 33:44.740
♫That year, that year♫

33:41.830 --> 33:42.660
Yes.

33:43.420 --> 33:44.390
One like you

33:44.410 --> 33:45.650
and the other like me.

33:45.390 --> 33:48.570
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

33:45.680 --> 33:47.280
You teach them swordsmanship.

33:47.550 --> 33:48.460
I...

33:49.070 --> 33:52.380
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

33:49.640 --> 33:51.160
I'll teach them how to steam buns.

33:53.510 --> 33:56.410
♫Layer after layer♫

33:53.920 --> 33:54.550
Okay.

33:55.330 --> 33:56.730
I'll teach them swordsmanship.

33:56.900 --> 33:59.780
♫Another year passed♫

33:57.690 --> 33:59.250
You teach them how to steam buns.

34:03.970 --> 34:07.610
♫Another year passed♫

35:22.060 --> 35:23.770
Soul Lotus:

35:23.800 --> 35:25.120
it's a healing flower

35:25.150 --> 35:26.900
with infinite life.

35:26.920 --> 35:28.360
Although your divine soul is dead,

35:28.390 --> 35:29.880
your body is still alive.

35:29.900 --> 35:31.610
It can be used by me

35:31.630 --> 35:33.780
and help me get the Divine Lord back.

35:33.860 --> 35:36.470
You didn't live for 60,000 years in vain.

36:13.470 --> 36:14.400
My lord,

36:14.850 --> 36:17.260
your Destiny Regalia is too powerful.

36:17.430 --> 36:18.600
I didn't expect

36:18.620 --> 36:20.740
even if with Soul Lotus,

36:20.770 --> 36:22.490
it's still difficult to repair.

36:26.050 --> 36:27.180
Turn left.

36:27.210 --> 36:28.220
Yes.

36:32.850 --> 36:33.890
Is that okay?

36:33.920 --> 36:35.830
A little to the right.

36:40.500 --> 36:41.620
This should be okay now, right?

36:44.270 --> 36:45.500
What are you looking at?

36:46.820 --> 36:49.010
Feels like something is missing.

36:49.040 --> 36:50.590
The decoration is fancy enough,

36:50.670 --> 36:52.020
but it's not lively enough.

36:52.050 --> 36:52.820
Little Demon,

36:52.850 --> 36:54.780
go to the back mountain and bring all the flowers here.

36:57.370 --> 36:58.460
Go.

36:59.220 --> 37:00.180
-Yes.
-Yes.

37:03.200 --> 37:04.760
Lady Tian Huo,

37:04.780 --> 37:06.530
you're very cooperative today.

37:06.560 --> 37:08.460
Don't act like that.

37:08.480 --> 37:09.890
I'm not cooperating with you.

37:09.920 --> 37:11.630
I must do my best

37:11.650 --> 37:13.130
for Bright Moon Palace's anniversary.

37:13.160 --> 37:14.910
So much so

37:14.940 --> 37:16.940
you're willing to hang lanterns under my command.

37:18.770 --> 37:20.850
Actually, saving Fan Yue is my wish.

37:20.870 --> 37:22.490
You don't have to thank me.

37:22.510 --> 37:24.050
Stop making wild guesses.

37:24.760 --> 37:26.550
If you ruin the celebration,

37:26.570 --> 37:27.740
I'll teach you a lesson.

37:29.550 --> 37:30.970
"I'll teach you a lesson."

37:32.210 --> 37:33.360
Ms. Bai,

37:33.380 --> 37:35.020
the osmanthus cakes you wanted are done.

37:35.050 --> 37:35.780
Thank you.

37:45.960 --> 37:46.920
Take a break.

37:47.540 --> 37:49.710
I asked the chef to make osmanthus cakes.

37:49.740 --> 37:50.820
Try it.

37:54.500 --> 37:55.380
All I heard this morning

37:55.410 --> 37:57.410
is your voice around the palace.

37:57.430 --> 37:59.320
How big is this ceremony going to be?

37:59.350 --> 38:01.460
This is the first anniversary we celebrate together.

38:01.480 --> 38:02.850
Of course it should be

38:02.880 --> 38:04.030
as lively as it can be!

38:04.050 --> 38:04.970
The first?

38:05.710 --> 38:07.100
You mean

38:07.130 --> 38:09.090
you want to spend the second and third one with me,

38:09.110 --> 38:09.990
forever and ever?

38:10.650 --> 38:11.820
What else?

38:11.850 --> 38:13.970
Who else do you want to celebrate it with besides me?

38:14.000 --> 38:15.170
No one else

38:15.190 --> 38:16.310
but you.

38:16.340 --> 38:17.450
That's more like it.

38:17.840 --> 38:19.140
I shan't waste my time with you.

38:19.160 --> 38:20.410
I'm going to supervise them.

38:20.440 --> 38:21.360
Take a good rest.

38:21.380 --> 38:22.650
Don't wander around.

38:22.680 --> 38:23.680
Okay.

38:35.770 --> 38:36.930
-Be careful.
-Okay.

38:36.960 --> 38:38.420
Make it straight.

38:38.880 --> 38:39.970
To the left.

38:48.390 --> 38:52.050
♫Writing wishes in the night sky♫

38:48.660 --> 38:51.250
This is the first time I've attended the celebration of a Demon Race.

38:53.170 --> 38:56.770
♫The clouds seal their approval for me♫

38:54.770 --> 38:56.480
The Cold Spring Palace has always been cold.

38:56.520 --> 38:57.960
There are no friendships,

38:57.220 --> 39:01.140
♫You walk towards me slowly♫

38:57.990 --> 38:59.820
much less celebrations.

39:00.970 --> 39:02.710
I don't know how to celebrate either.

39:02.400 --> 39:05.140
♫Time stops♫

39:02.840 --> 39:04.720
Let's take a good look at

39:04.740 --> 39:06.430
what the celebration of Bright Moon Palace is like.

39:06.490 --> 39:10.320
♫The brightest star in the night sky♫

39:10.820 --> 39:14.530
♫Is willing to extinguish for you♫

39:15.440 --> 39:19.310
♫Because the starlight in your eyes♫

39:20.160 --> 39:23.390
♫Lights up my long night♫

39:26.940 --> 39:30.280
♫I'm afraid tomorrow is too far♫

39:31.110 --> 39:34.530
♫Love you at every moment♫

39:36.050 --> 39:37.760
♫Don't miss me♫

39:38.030 --> 39:42.740
♫I'll always be by your side♫

39:39.650 --> 39:41.150
It's already pretty lively outside.

39:41.180 --> 39:42.470
Let's go.

39:43.500 --> 39:44.870
You're going just like this?

39:44.450 --> 39:47.580
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

39:45.500 --> 39:46.570
How else should it be?

39:47.500 --> 39:49.210
Today is a big day for the palace.

39:49.150 --> 39:52.550
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

39:49.280 --> 39:51.060
You're Demon King of the Polar Region and Master of Bright Moon.

39:51.090 --> 39:52.700
Of course you should be different.

39:52.720 --> 39:53.880
How?

39:54.140 --> 39:56.030
♫Every starlight♫

39:55.020 --> 39:55.860
Watch me.

39:57.010 --> 40:00.420
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

40:03.300 --> 40:05.030
The new clothes you prepared

40:03.440 --> 40:07.670
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

40:05.060 --> 40:06.900
is more flamboyant than I would normally be.

40:07.290 --> 40:08.360
I did it on purpose.

40:08.420 --> 40:11.820
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

40:09.110 --> 40:10.950
I want to show them

40:10.970 --> 40:12.090
how beautiful

40:12.120 --> 40:13.200
our Demon King is.

40:12.600 --> 40:14.320
♫Every starlight♫

40:15.140 --> 40:19.030
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

40:55.590 --> 40:56.360
My lord...

40:57.860 --> 40:58.710
My lord.

40:59.610 --> 41:00.880
We did it.

41:01.490 --> 41:02.990
We did it!

41:03.140 --> 41:05.150
We did it!

41:36.900 --> 41:37.710
Fan Yue.

41:38.560 --> 41:39.290
Fan Yue.

41:40.310 --> 41:41.380
What happened?

41:42.220 --> 41:43.410
The seven stars are all gone.

41:44.090 --> 41:46.030
I didn't manage to escape after all.

41:46.860 --> 41:47.760
No.

41:48.470 --> 41:49.510
I'll go make more

41:49.530 --> 41:50.570
first-grade elixir.

41:50.600 --> 41:52.070
Even without Master's tortoise shell,

41:52.090 --> 41:53.800
I can definitely still cultivate it!

41:59.320 --> 42:00.340
My demonic power...

42:01.460 --> 42:02.550
is exhausted...

42:05.990 --> 42:07.400
Where is your demonic power?

42:07.730 --> 42:08.840
How did this happen?

42:09.600 --> 42:10.850
I thought God

42:10.920 --> 42:12.670
gave us one more chance.

42:13.050 --> 42:15.360
I thought I could continue keep you company.

42:17.480 --> 42:18.530
I didn't expect...

42:19.020 --> 42:20.900
I still can't change the ending.

42:23.400 --> 42:24.560
Stop saying that.

42:25.480 --> 42:26.870
I don't want to hear it.

42:27.700 --> 42:29.600
You promised me

42:31.230 --> 42:33.020
you'll always be by my side.

42:34.490 --> 42:35.650
I'm here, Shuo.

42:36.490 --> 42:37.760
I'll always be here.

42:38.960 --> 42:40.840
Do you remember what I told you?

42:42.310 --> 42:43.670
Every one of us

42:43.700 --> 42:45.380
has their own fate.

42:45.850 --> 42:47.040
But what happened

42:47.780 --> 42:49.630
will never be meaningless.

42:51.290 --> 42:53.060
If meeting you

42:53.090 --> 42:54.850
was fate,

42:55.190 --> 42:57.380
I won't resent fate

42:58.660 --> 43:00.420
for letting our encounter

43:01.000 --> 43:02.580
be so short.

43:03.930 --> 43:04.930
Because...

43:05.560 --> 43:07.310
Fan Yue meeting Bai Shuo

43:08.370 --> 43:09.830
and falling in love with Bai Shuo

43:10.620 --> 43:13.090
is the luckiest thing in my life.

43:14.960 --> 43:16.020
Promise me.

43:17.000 --> 43:18.230
Don't be sad.

43:25.490 --> 43:30.260
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

43:30.410 --> 43:33.230
Everyone has been looking forward to tonight.

43:33.790 --> 43:35.460
I have too.

43:33.910 --> 43:39.200
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

43:36.500 --> 43:38.020
Let's not be party poopers

43:38.200 --> 43:39.310
and enjoy

43:40.660 --> 43:42.680
this anniversary celebration, shall we?

43:41.880 --> 43:49.440
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

43:50.270 --> 43:55.560
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫
